  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p>Cut the<strong> potatoes</strong> (skins on) into wedges, put them on a baking tray, drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and season with <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put them in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crispy&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and grate the <strong>beetroot </strong>into a sieve, over a bowl, then press to release any excess <strong>juice</strong>&nbsp;(you'll use this later!)</p>\r\n<p>Tip: try and squeeze as much juice out as you can, this will help the beet burgers stick together</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>tarragon</strong> finely, including the stalks&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Peel and chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Pat the <strong>feta</strong> dry with kitchen paper and break it up into small pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Peel and slice the <strong>red</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated&nbsp;</strong><strong>beetroot,</strong> <strong>garlic</strong>,<strong> feta</strong>, <strong>breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, half of the <strong>tarragon</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> in a large bowl and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Slice the <strong>ciabattas</strong> in half and then into 4 (see picture) - this will give you 4 sliders each</p>\r\n<p>Heat a wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1-2 tbsp <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add&nbsp;the <strong>onion</strong>&nbsp;with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5 min or until slightly softened&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Reduce the heat to medium-low, add the <strong>beetroot juice</strong> and cook for a further 5 min</p>\r\n<p>Once the onions are cooked, transfer them to a dish, wipe the pan clean and reserve it for later</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/706.-step--5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
